{"lastModified":1770163766142,"uri":"c::21836669044::vessel::cec88b00-8cf9-11f0-a72e-a5107c6da59f","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: Bahamas, United States of America- New England, United States of America- Florida East Coast, United States of America - North East\nWinter Operating Area: Caribbean Virgin Islands (United States/British Virgin Islands), Bahamas, Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Windwards, United States of America- Florida East Coast, Canary Islands, Caribbean Virgin Islands (United States), Caribbean Virgin Islands (British Virgin Islands)\n\nLuxury 88' Azimut Yacht Charter in Florida, Bahamas, and The Keys\nEmbark on an unforgettable voyage aboard the spectacular 88' Azimut Yacht, a pinnacle of Italian design and luxury, available for charter in the stunning waters of Florida, the Bahamas, and the Florida Keys. This 2022-refitted vessel, part of the Azimut Flybridge series, combines sleek aesthetics, cutting-edge technology, and unparalleled comfort, making it the ideal choice for discerning travelers seeking a premium yachting experience. Whether you're planning a vibrant day trip, a lavish event, or an extended escape, this yacht delivers an extraordinary blend of adventure and indulgence for up to 12 cruising guests or 10 overnight guests.\n\nKey Features\nSophisticated Design and Spacious Decks\nThe 88' Azimut boasts a sleek, modern exterior with clean lines and expansive windows, creating a striking profile that exudes elegance. Its deep-V hull ensures stability and smooth cruising, even in varied sea conditions. The yacht features multiple exterior spaces, including a spacious flybridge with panoramic views, a hot tub, and a bar with stools, perfect for entertaining or relaxing under the stars. The teak-decked aft deck offers an ideal setting for al fresco dining, while the foredeck provides plush sun pads for soaking up the sun. The 2022 refit enhances the yacht’s contemporary aesthetic with updated finishes and state-of-the-art amenities.\n\nThe main salon is a masterpiece of luxury, featuring high-end materials like fine woods, polished surfaces, and plush furnishings. Large windows flood the interior with natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. The salon includes a formal dining area and a lounge equipped with Direct TV, Satellite TV, and Streaming TV, ensuring entertainment for all guests. The Bluetooth sound system allows you to set the perfect mood with your favorite music, whether hosting a lively gathering or enjoying a quiet evening on the water.\n\nLuxurious Accommodations\nThe yacht’s four staterooms are designed to provide a serene and indulgent retreat for up to 10 overnight guests. Each cabin features en-suite bathrooms, climate control, and luxurious amenities. The master suite is a highlight, offering a king-size bed, panoramic windows, and ample storage for a hotel-like experience. The additional cabins—one queen, two twin side-by-sides, and two Pullmans—are equally well-appointed, ensuring comfort and privacy for families, friends, or couples. The 2022 refit ensures all interiors are pristine, with modern fixtures and premium linens.","blueprint":{"name":"SKY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::cec88b00-8cf9-11f0-a72e-a5107c6da59f::assets::b5785770-8cfe-11f0-8cdd-d302341aa37f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cec88b00-8cf9-11f0-a72e-a5107c6da59f::assets::b5779420-8cfe-11f0-8b08-6b96c2a6aaa0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cec88b00-8cf9-11f0-a72e-a5107c6da59f::assets::b533fb70-8cfe-11f0-8b07-6b96c2a6aaa0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cec88b00-8cf9-11f0-a72e-a5107c6da59f::assets::b5763490-8cfe-11f0-8cdd-d302341aa37f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cec88b00-8cf9-11f0-a72e-a5107c6da59f::assets::b5355b00-8cfe-11f0-8b08-6b96c2a6aaa0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cec88b00-8cf9-11f0-a72e-a5107c6da59f::assets::b576d0d0-8cfe-11f0-8cdd-d302341aa37f/{imageVariant}",